Class ApplicationTopologyCache

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.TopologyCache
      com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.ApplicationTopologyCache

public class ApplicationTopologyCache
extends TopologyCache

Provides the interface for the model-level topology caching that can utilized by topology publishers. This extends the base TopologyCache by adding support for the separate caching of ConfigurationUnits
